snippet.title: Dionne Warwick on Reuniting Taylor Swift with Her Scarf | Drew's News
snippet.description:
Living legend Dionne Warwick joins Drew and Ross Mathews to discuss Adele's new residency, Dionne's campaign to reunite Taylor Swift with her missing scarf, her collab with Chance the Rapper. Plus Ms. Dionne gives our audience life advice to end the year.
